text:
The 2016 United States presidential election in Maine was held on 8 November 2016. It was part of the 2016 United States presidential election, in which all other states plus the District of Columbia voted.
Polling.
Below is a table with the polling results in Maine. Maine as a whole has voted Democrat in the general election since 1992.
Democratic.
The Democratic caucus occurred on 6 March 2016.
Republican.
The Republican caucus occurred on 5 March 2016.
